{"tid":764044,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[暑期治癒神作] 我的暑假系列","createTime":"2018-08-01T15:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T18:52:36.000Z","uid":37125,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df54250fb68d86ca4fd364a049ecea94d8b52dd3","tid":764044,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/05/Boku_no_Natsuyasumi_Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F0%2F05%2FBoku_no_Natsuyasumi_Cover.jpg&h=8398778a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/511JY05QTGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F511JY05QTGL.jpg&h=42d32232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61OAHchMv0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61OAHchMv0L.jpg&h=1feaeaa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/5195y6uSwtL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F5195y6uSwtL.jpg&h=d54c49bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nぼくのなつやすみ, 每集都係講述主角細個嗰時去親朋戚友屋企過暑假嘅經歷. 依個系列應該都算係 Open World game, 你可以剩係著住條底褲通山跑, 又可以潛水尋寶, 捉甲蟲嚟同啲細路對戰, 儲怪獸擦膠....... 多嘢做到根本一日廿四小時唔夠用. 最重要係啲有趣小學雞劇情, 應該會令你諗翻起唔小嘢.<br />\n<br />\n依隻 game 絕對可以令你從依個加速世代嘅繃緊情緒入面暫時行開下.  可惜嘅係依個系列只係得日文版, 不過好似得第四集先有漢化版. 如果要試嘅其實都應該係試第四集, 因為依集應該係最多嘢玩同儲嘅一集.  <br />\n<br />\n得閒可以搵嚟試試, 隻 game 真係非常有趣同治癒."},{"pid":"ea5fe638755d09594ea519a483f8ff6faa714459","tid":764044,"uid":127821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T16:40:57.000Z","msg":"個人最鍾意第二集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac297d9817b7fc6c5ca0467b3f327f2b7e210e76